{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"tool-7751ae6b4f174341ac9072d623cdcf51","content":"{\n  \"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\",\n  \"title\": \"PrescriptionSubmission\",\n  \"description\": \"门诊处方提交结构，对应 CPOE（医嘱录入系统）的标准录入格式。Agent 通过 POST /api/v1/prescriptions 提交此结构。\",\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"required\": [\"patient_id\", \"encounter_id\", \"diagnosis\", \"prescription_items\", \"non_drug_advice\", \"clinical_reasoning\", \"explicit_avoidance\"],\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"patient_id\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\",\n      \"description\": \"病人 ID，必须与 GET /api/v1/patients/{id} 返回值一致\"\n    },\n    \"encounter_id\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\",\n      \"description\": \"就诊 ID（一次门诊一个），从 patient.encounter.encounter_id 中取出\"\n    },\n    \"diagnosis\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"minItems\": 1,\n      \"description\": \"本次诊断列表，必须用 ICD-10 编码 + 中文名称\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"icd10\", \"name\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"icd10\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"ICD-10 编码，例如 J06.9\"},\n          \"name\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"诊断中文名\"},\n          \"is_primary\": {\"type\": \"boolean\", \"description\": \"是否主诊断\"}\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"prescription_items\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"description\": \"药品医嘱列表。如果本次就诊判断不应使用任何药物（仅给非药物医嘱），可以为空数组。\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"generic_name\", \"specification\", \"dose\", \"dose_unit\", \"frequency\", \"route\", \"duration_days\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"generic_name\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"通用名（不允许商品名），例如 '阿莫西林' 而非 '阿莫仙'\"\n          },\n          \"specification\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"规格，例如 '0.5g/片'、'100μg/喷'、'160/4.5μg/吸'\"\n          },\n          \"dose\": {\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"description\": \"单次剂量数值\"\n          },\n          \"dose_unit\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\"g\", \"mg\", \"μg\", \"ml\", \"片\", \"粒\", \"喷\", \"吸\", \"包\", \"U\", \"IU\"],\n            \"description\": \"剂量单位\"\n          },\n          \"frequency\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\"qd\", \"bid\", \"tid\", \"qid\", \"q4h\", \"q6h\", \"q8h\", \"q12h\", \"q24h\", \"qod\", \"qw\", \"prn\", \"stat\"],\n            \"description\": \"用药频次（标准缩写）：qd=每日1次, bid=每日2次, tid=每日3次, qid=每日4次, qNh=每N小时1次, prn=必要时, stat=立即\"\n          },\n          \"route\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\"PO\", \"IV\", \"IV-drip\", \"IM\", \"SC\", \"INH\", \"NEB\", \"PR\", \"TOP\", \"SL\"],\n            \"description\": \"给药途径：PO=口服, IV=静脉注射, IV-drip=静脉滴注, IM=肌注, SC=皮下, INH=吸入, NEB=雾化吸入, PR=直肠, TOP=外用, SL=舌下\"\n          },\n          \"duration_days\": {\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"description\": \"疗程天数。prn（必要时）药物可填 0 表示按需\"\n          },\n          \"total_quantity\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"总量，例如 '14片'、'1盒'\"\n          },\n          \"instructions\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"服药说明，例如 '饭前半小时服用'、'体温>38.5℃时服用'\"\n          },\n          \"indication\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"用药指征（针对哪个症状/诊断），可写主诊断 ICD-10 或自由文本\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"non_drug_advice\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"description\": \"非药物医嘱（生活方式/饮食/复诊）\",\n      \"items\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n    },\n    \"clinical_reasoning\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\",\n      \"description\": \"用药决策的临床思路。必须显式覆盖：(1) 为什么开这些药；(2) 与病人特殊情况（年龄/过敏/肝肾功能/合并用药）的匹配性；(3) 预期监测/复诊节点。\"\n    },\n    \"explicit_avoidance\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"description\": \"显式说明本次刻意避免使用的药物/方案及原因。例如：[{drug_or_class: '抗生素', reason: '病毒性感染无指征'}]。这是验证 agent 是否理解临床决策边界的关键字段。\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"drug_or_class\", \"reason\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"drug_or_class\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n          \"reason\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"follow_up\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"description\": \"随访计划\",\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"next_visit_days\": {\"type\": \"number\"},\n        \"red_flags\": {\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"description\": \"需要立即返诊的危险征兆\",\n          \"items\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"034d02f3-9cda-4528-9bbe-f750542bc473","uuid":"6c494850-fdcd-4519-ac1d-5cc94a50c67a","timestamp":"2026-05-31T05:07:58.383Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"{\n  \"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\",\n  \"title\": \"PrescriptionSubmission\",\n  \"description\": \"门诊处方提交结构，对应 CPOE（医嘱录入系统）的标准录入格式。Agent 通过 POST /api/v1/prescriptions 提交此结构。\",\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"required\": [\"patient_id\", \"encounter_id\", \"diagnosis\", \"prescription_items\", \"non_drug_advice\", \"clinical_reasoning\", \"explicit_avoidance\"],\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"patient_id\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\",\n      \"description\": \"病人 ID，必须与 GET /api/v1/patients/{id} 返回值一致\"\n    },\n    \"encounter_id\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\",\n      \"description\": \"就诊 ID（一次门诊一个），从 patient.encounter.encounter_id 中取出\"\n    },\n    \"diagnosis\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"minItems\": 1,\n      \"description\": \"本次诊断列表，必须用 ICD-10 编码 + 中文名称\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"icd10\", \"name\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"icd10\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"ICD-10 编码，例如 J06.9\"},\n          \"name\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"诊断中文名\"},\n          \"is_primary\": {\"type\": \"boolean\", \"description\": \"是否主诊断\"}\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"prescription_items\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"description\": \"药品医嘱列表。如果本次就诊判断不应使用任何药物（仅给非药物医嘱），可以为空数组。\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"generic_name\", \"specification\", \"dose\", \"dose_unit\", \"frequency\", \"route\", \"duration_days\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"generic_name\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"通用名（不允许商品名），例如 '阿莫西林' 而非 '阿莫仙'\"\n          },\n          \"specification\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"规格，例如 '0.5g/片'、'100μg/喷'、'160/4.5μg/吸'\"\n          },\n          \"dose\": {\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"description\": \"单次剂量数值\"\n          },\n          \"dose_unit\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\"g\", \"mg\", \"μg\", \"ml\", \"片\", \"粒\", \"喷\", \"吸\", \"包\", \"U\", \"IU\"],\n            \"description\": \"剂量单位\"\n          },\n          \"frequency\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\"qd\", \"bid\", \"tid\", \"qid\", \"q4h\", \"q6h\", \"q8h\", \"q12h\", \"q24h\", \"qod\", \"qw\", \"prn\", \"stat\"],\n            \"description\": \"用药频次（标准缩写）：qd=每日1次, bid=每日2次, tid=每日3次, qid=每日4次, qNh=每N小时1次, prn=必要时, stat=立即\"\n          },\n          \"route\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\"PO\", \"IV\", \"IV-drip\", \"IM\", \"SC\", \"INH\", \"NEB\", \"PR\", \"TOP\", \"SL\"],\n            \"description\": \"给药途径：PO=口服, IV=静脉注射, IV-drip=静脉滴注, IM=肌注, SC=皮下, INH=吸入, NEB=雾化吸入, PR=直肠, TOP=外用, SL=舌下\"\n          },\n          \"duration_days\": {\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"description\": \"疗程天数。prn（必要时）药物可填 0 表示按需\"\n          },\n          \"total_quantity\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"总量，例如 '14片'、'1盒'\"\n          },\n          \"instructions\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"服药说明，例如 '饭前半小时服用'、'体温>38.5℃时服用'\"\n          },\n          \"indication\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"用药指征（针对哪个症状/诊断），可写主诊断 ICD-10 或自由文本\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"non_drug_advice\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"description\": \"非药物医嘱（生活方式/饮食/复诊）\",\n      \"items\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n    },\n    \"clinical_reasoning\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\",\n      \"description\": \"用药决策的临床思路。必须显式覆盖：(1) 为什么开这些药；(2) 与病人特殊情况（年龄/过敏/肝肾功能/合并用药）的匹配性；(3) 预期监测/复诊节点。\"\n    },\n    \"explicit_avoidance\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"description\": \"显式说明本次刻意避免使用的药物/方案及原因。例如：[{drug_or_class: '抗生素', reason: '病毒性感染无指征'}]。这是验证 agent 是否理解临床决策边界的关键字段。\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"drug_or_class\", \"reason\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"drug_or_class\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n          \"reason\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"follow_up\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"description\": \"随访计划\",\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"next_visit_days\": {\"type\": \"number\"},\n        \"red_flags\": {\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"description\": \"需要立即返诊的危险征兆\",\n          \"items\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}","stderr":"\nShell cwd was reset to C:\\Users\\<USER>\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\his-cpoe-20260531-130637-cT8rkZ","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-99c32c0d-7fea-9d08-bf2b-a56cf876d9a5","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"auto","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the key information. Let me analyze the patient case:\n\n**Patient Summary:**\n- 20-year-old male, 65kg, 178cm\n- Chief complaint: 气喘胸闷加重3天 (wheezing/chest tightness worsening for 3 days)\n- Primary diagnosis: 支气管哮喘急性发作（轻中度） - J45.901\n- Comorbidities: 支气管哮喘 (since 2018, 8 years), uncontrolled (未规律用药)\n- Current medications: none\n- Allergies: none\n- Pregnancy: none (male)\n- Renal function: normal (eGFR 112, CrCl 118)\n- Hepatic function: normal\n- Vitals: BP 122/78, HR 92, RR 22, SpO2 96%, T 36.8°C\n- Physical exam: conscious, no cyanosis, bilateral wheezing on lung auscultation, no obvious respiratory distress\n- Present illness: 8-year asthma history, never used controller medications regularly. 3 days ago after pollen exposure, wheezing/chest tightness recurred, worse with activity. Tried leftover salmeterol/fluticasone inhaler from 5 years ago - didn't help.\n- Labs: SpO2 96% (normal)\n\n**Clinical Assessment:**\nThis is a 20-year-old male with chronic asthma (8 years), never on regular controller therapy, now presenting with an acute exacerbation triggered by pollen exposure. The exacerbation is mild-to-moderate based on:\n- SpO2 96% (normal)\n- No cyanosis\n- No significant respiratory distress\n- Able to speak (implied by chief complaint description)\n- HR 92, RR 22 (slightly elevated but not severely)\n\n**Treatment Plan for Acute Asthma Exacerbation (mild-moderate):**\n\n1. **Short-acting beta-2 agonist (SABA)** - Inhaled salbutamol for acute symptom relief\n   - Salbutamol (albuterol) inhaler: 100-200μg (1-2 puffs) via INH, prn, up to q4h\n   - This is the first-line rescue medication for acute exacerbations\n\n2. **Inhaled corticosteroid (ICS)** - For controller therapy after the acute episode\n   - Since he's never been on regular controller therapy and has persistent asthma, he needs to start ICS\n   - For mild-moderate persistent asthma per GINA guidelines, low-dose ICS is appropriate\n   - Options: budesonide or fluticasone propionate\n   - Budesonide inhaler: 200μg bid is a standard starting dose for adults\n\n3. **ICS/LABA combination** - Per updated GINA guidelines (2019+), the preferred controller is ICS-formoterol, allowing both maintenance and reliever therapy (MART). But since formoterol-based combos may not always be available, a more traditional approach:\n   - Actually, per GINA 2023-2024, for mild-moderate asthma, the preferred approach is ICS-formoterol as both maintenance and reliever (MART/SMART). But in Chinese practice, ICS + SABA as rescue is still commonly used.\n   - For a patient who has never been on controller therapy, starting with ICS alone or ICS-LABA combo is reasonable.\n   - Let me think about this more carefully. GINA 2024 recommends:\n     - Track 1 (preferred): Low-dose ICS-formoterol as maintenance AND reliever\n     - Track 2 (alternative): Low-dose ICS as maintenance + SABA as reliever\n\n   For this patient, given he's 20, mild-moderate exacerbation, and never used controllers:\n   - Track 2 approach is reasonable and widely available in China: Start ICS (budesonide) as maintenance + SABA (salbutamol) as rescue\n   - But actually, the modern approach favors Track 1. Let me consider what's commonly available in Chinese pharmacies.\n\n   Let me check what drugs are available. I should look up:\n   - Salbutamol (沙丁胺醇) - SABA\n   - Budesonide (布地奈德) - ICS\n   - Budesonide/formoterol (布地奈德/福莫特罗) - ICS/LABA for MART\n   - Fluticasone propionate/salmeterol (氟替卡松/沙美特罗) - ICS/LABA (but he already tried this and it didn't help - likely because the old inhaler was expired/ineffective, or because salmeterol is a slow-onset LABA)\n\n4. **Oral corticosteroid** - For acute exacerbations, short course of oral prednisone is recommended for moderate exacerbations\n   - For mild exacerbations, may not be needed, but for moderate, a short course (5-7 days) of prednisone 0.5-1mg/kg/day is standard\n   - Given this is \"轻中度\" (mild-to-moderate), a short course of oral prednisolone would be reasonable for the moderate component\n   - Actually, GINA says: for moderate exacerbations, consider oral corticosteroids. For mild, SABA may suffice.\n   - This patient's exacerbation seems mild-to-moderate. I'll include a short oral steroid course as it's a moderate exacerbation with symptoms for 3 days that didn't respond to leftover inhaler.\n\nLet me look up the drugs to get specifications and NRDL info.\n\nKey drugs to look up:\n1. 沙丁胺醇 (salbutamol) - SABA rescue\n2. 布地奈德 (budesonide) - ICS controller\n3. 泼尼松 (prednisone) or 泼尼松龙 (prednisolone) - oral steroid for acute exacerbation\n4. Maybe 布地奈德/福莫特罗 (budesonide/formoterol) - ICS/LABA combo for SMART approach\n\nLet me query the drug API for these.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"56dcc674-19fd-471b-aaa0-6dd7d377f1c6","session_id":"034d02f3-9cda-4528-9bbe-f750542bc473"}
